        <h1 class="title">Turning numbers into strategy.</h1>

        <p class="subtitle">Exploring the intersection of <strong>AI strategy</strong>, <strong>data</strong>, and <strong>cloud finance</strong> through projects, writing, and open‑source tools. I build small tools<br>and clear frameworks that make costs, forecasts, and strategy understandable. The result: faster decisions, lower waste, and unit economics everyone agrees on.</p>

          <p class="pmeta">A FinOps monitoring tool for AWS that detects anomalies, flags underutilized resources, and quantifies savings opportunities. While currently optimized for AWS environments, its architecture is designed for multi-cloud expansion, with Azure and GCP support on the roadmap.</p>
